{"h":[{"d":[{"f":"群體，種類(動物)。","e":["￹`Mahapinang~ `ko~ `kasalekad~ `no~ `finacadan~.￺￻各族群不一樣。","￹`Adihay~ `ko~ `kasasiromaroma~ `a~ `kasalekad~ `no~ `'a'adopen~.￺￻動物的種類繁多。","￹`Midipotay~ `to~ `'a'adopen~ `a~ `kasalekad~.￺￻動物保育團體。"],"s":["`kasarekad~"],"r":["`kasalekalekad~"]},{"f":"段落、單元、章節。","e":["￹`Kasalekad~ `nona~ o`ho~ng.￺￻這本書的章節。"]}]}],"stem":"lekad","t":"kasalekad"}